'''香脂豆'''（{{lang-xm|Myroxylon peruiferum}}；{{lang-es|quina-quina}}）是[[豆科|豆科]][[香脂豆属|香脂豆属]]的模式种，间断分布于[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]南部至[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]北部、[[巴西|巴西]]南部的[[拉美|拉美]]地区。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=A revision of the genus ''Myroxylon'' (Leguminosae: Papilionoideae)|url=http://link.springer.com/10.1007/s12225-015-9604-7|last=Sartori|first=Ângela Lúcia Bagnatori|last2=Lewis|first2=Gwilym P.|date=2015-12|journal=Kew Bulletin|issue=4|doi=10.1007/s12225-015-9604-7|volume=70|pages=48|issn=0075-5974|last3=de Freitas Mansano|first3=Vidal|last4=de Azevedo Tozzi|first4=Ana Maria Goulart}}</ref>

种加词的意思是“产[[秘鲁香|秘鲁香]]的”，得名于旧时人们对本种的误解。<ref name="L.f.">{{Cite book|title=Supplementum Plantarum|last=Linnaeus filius|first=Carl|publisher=Orphanotropheum|year=1781|location=Braunschweig|pages=233|url=https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/411266#page/248/mode/1up|access-date=2021-03-10|archive-date=2021-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210602214907/https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/411266#page/248/mode/1up|dead-url=no}}</ref>其实秘鲁香是同属的另一种植物[[秘鲁香树|秘鲁香树]]（{{sn|''Myroxylon balsamum'' var. ''pereirae''}}）的树脂提取物。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=On the ''Myrospermum'' of Sonsonate, from which balsam of Peru, white balsam, and balsamito are obtained|last=Pereira|first=Jonathan|url=https://babel.hathitrust.org/cgi/pt?id=iau.31858018389811&view=1up&seq=296|journal=The Pharmaceutical Journal and Transactions|issue=8|year=1850|volume=10|page=280-290}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2016-05-31|title=Assessment report on ''Myroxylon balsamum'' (L.) Harms var. ''pereirae'' (Royle) Harms, balsamum|url=https://www.ema.europa.eu/en/documents/herbal-report/final-assessment-report-myroxylon-balsamum-l-harms-var-pereirae-royle-harms-balsamum_en.pdf|access-date=2021-03-10|website=European Medicines Agency|publisher=Committee on Herbal Medicinal Products (HMPC)|archive-date=2019-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327185503/https://www.ema.europa.eu/en/documents/herbal-report/final-assessment-report-myroxylon-balsamum-l-harms-var-pereirae-royle-harms-balsamum_en.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

